{"tid":1211594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612 目標達成 之後要點做 真心想知？","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:04:50.000Z","uid":201220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"187615b78f01d23a5ea021cc5716edd7aae76d05","tid":1211594,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"對於今日要達成既目的好明確 <br />\n二讀三讀個會開唔成 可以話係階段性成功<br />\n得到各階級人士 意外壞車 都無比藉口政府升級行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有朋友仲係出面 一定要勸佢地退落黎</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n跟住落黎<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每發起一次 都要有明確目標 </span></span><br />\n唔好比有心人聲東擊西 好想大家清楚返 今次係要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">徹回送中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩下台同港獨口號 只會比位人入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平民百姓手無寸鐵 基本上只可以以智謀取勝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/12/235721_db99ef8101409802589a2e985c0c2fbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F12%2F235721_db99ef8101409802589a2e985c0c2fbe.png&h=724a70d4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}